11:53.922 --> 11:55.339
An energy drink?

11:55.340 --> 11:56.506
Seriously?

12:04.974 --> 12:06.266
Yup.

12:06.267 --> 12:09.372
Just a normal, ordinary,
nothing special about it,

12:09.397 --> 12:11.021
energy drink.

12:15.109 --> 12:16.360
Kanpai.

12:53.698 --> 12:56.359
