12:57.425 --> 12:59.442
Wh... what happened?

12:59.467 --> 13:02.739
When you drink Impulse
9, you're stretching time.

13:02.740 --> 13:04.408
The harder you stretch...

13:06.077 --> 13:07.744
the harder you snap back.

13:07.745 --> 13:10.270
This time you lost about an hour.

13:10.915 --> 13:13.709
It's like being blackout
drunk, minus the drunk part.

13:13.710 --> 13:15.752
Holy shit.

13:15.753 --> 13:17.921
$500 a bottle, Speedrun.

13:17.922 --> 13:19.644
That is...

13:19.669 --> 13:20.924
