13:31.644 --> 13:32.769
But is it wrong?

13:36.566 --> 13:38.949
Roy doesn't seem to think so.

13:39.235 --> 13:40.982
Hey, bro, what's up?

13:41.109 --> 13:43.280
What's that, another case of Impulse

13:43.281 --> 13:44.656
for the match tomorrow?

13:44.657 --> 13:45.741
You got it.

13:45.742 --> 13:47.993
Cash only, ATM's in the front.

13:49.245 --> 13:51.597
Yeah, I'm still here.

13:51.622 --> 13:53.285
Nope, nobody you know.

14:05.053 --> 14:06.386
Welcome to the final round

14:06.387 --> 14:08.722
of the Chino Hills Field
of Fire Regional Tournament.

14:08.723 --> 14:09.806
In just a few moments

14:09.807 --> 14:12.059
