14:28.826 --> 14:30.609
Don't worry, babe...

14:30.995 --> 14:33.455
there's plenty of me to go around.

14:33.456 --> 14:35.303
Go, Speedrun.

14:35.328 --> 14:36.708
Yeah, Speedrun.

15:26.912 --> 15:29.219
Now Speedrun Hernandez is on fire.

15:29.220 --> 15:30.637
She's having the game of her life

15:30.638 --> 15:32.764
but, unfortunately, it's just not enough

15:32.765 --> 15:34.850
