kids before gate duty tonight?

18:39.494 --> 18:41.411
- Val?
- Sure.

18:41.412 --> 18:43.246
Look, Daddy, I found a neat rock!

18:43.247 --> 18:45.248
No, no, that's a poop,
sweetie, put that back.

18:45.249 --> 18:46.625
No, I want it!

18:46.626 --> 18:47.959
Tell you what, you give that to Mom,

18:47.960 --> 18:49.414
you can have it back after school, okay?

18:49.438 --> 18:50.546
- Okay.
- All right.

18:50.547 --> 18:52.631
There you go, Mommy... Mommy?

18:52.632 --> 18:53.757
There we are.

18:53.758 --> 18:55.008
Okay.

18:55.009 --> 18:56.593
All right, kids.

18:56.594 --> 18:58.303
Have a good day.

18:58.304 --> 18:59.471
Hi, guys!

18:59.472 --> 19:01.598
Hi, now take your seats, go on.

19:01.599 --> 19:04.309
