you see a Death Lizard?

19:04.310 --> 19:06.478
Run and hide!

19:06.479 --> 19:09.158
Shoot, I'm gonna be late.

19:09.193 --> 19:10.777
Evan, I need to talk to you.

19:10.802 --> 19:12.442
Okay, quick, what's up?

19:12.443 --> 19:13.777
Sheriff Val, did you hear?

19:13.778 --> 19:15.487
- Sheriff?
- Jana's husband

19:15.488 --> 19:16.488
