- Can you believe it?

19:22.536 --> 19:23.995
Oy, get back here!

19:23.996 --> 19:25.830
Look.

19:25.831 --> 19:26.915
Let's go, let's go.

19:26.916 --> 19:28.291
Let's go, now!

19:28.292 --> 19:30.960
Sheriff, Sheriff, caught
myself a no-good 'Pulser.

19:30.961 --> 19:32.504
What's going on, who are you people?

19:32.505 --> 19:34.673
What... why is it the apocalypse?

19:34.674 --> 19:35.965
I'll tell you why it's the apocalypse.

19:35.966 --> 19:38.301
It's because thoughtless
slackers like you

19:38.302 --> 19:40.679
chugged too much Impulse
and when you snapped back,

19:40.680 --> 19:42.222
the world went to shit, that's why.

19:42.223 --> 19:44.474
I was... I was studying for finals.

19:44.475 --> 19:45.850
"I was studying for fi..."

19:45.851 --> 19:47.394
